text.tspan: Henry VII was a clever and accomplished monarch. He
married the right woman, married his daughters to the right
men, and convieved one of the most notorious monarchs in
British History *cough cough Henry VII cough cough*
The interesting about Henry VII is his mother, Margaret
Beaufort. Honestly... its the most interesting part. A
descendent of two major royal lines, and one strong
woman, she is what got Henry on the throne of England.
